snippet.title: Popcorn Talk
snippet.description:
Popcorn Talk Network is the online broadcast network with programming dedicated exclusively to movie discussion, news, interviews and commentary. Popcorn Talk Network is comprised of the leading members and personalities of the film press and community.


Current Roster or Shows:
-Disney Movie News
-Anatomy of a Movie
-Profiles with Malone and Mantz
-Box Office Breakdown
-Jedi Alliance
-Meet the Movie Press
-Guilty Movie Pleasures
-Marvel Movie News
-DC Movie News
-Otaku Movie Anatomy
-Action Movie Anatomy
-Watchalong Series!
-The Comic Con Survival Show
-Covino & Rich's Thursday Night Live

Also check out: 
- http://www.site.afterbuzztv.com
- http://www.blackhollywoodlive.com
- http://www.bookcircleonline.com
